text: Hehe, that was fun, wasn't it...?
Is it the kind of laughter that comes from reminiscing?

Wearing that costume, singing and dancing,
it made all the difficult things just fly away...

I'm glad Chiyuki enjoyed herself.
And... I feel like I understand that feeling too.

When you dive in with determination, it's often more enjoyable
than you expect... I think those kinds of experiences exist.

As one of ALSTROEMERIA, I'll do my best.
Please continue to watch over me...!
